msgid "# Expert Parallelism Load Balancer (EPLB)"
msgstr "# 专家并行负载均衡器 (EPLB)"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"Expert balancing for MoE (Mixture of Experts) models in LLM (Large Language)"
" serving is essential for optimal performance. Dynamically changing experts "
"during inference can negatively impact TTFT (Time To First Token) and TPOT "
"(Time Per Output Token) due to stop-the-world operations. Our solution aims "
"to minimize the negative impacts caused by the operation."
msgstr ""
"在LLM（大语言模型）服务中，对MoE（混合专家）模型进行专家均衡对于实现最佳性能至关重要。推理过程中动态调整专家会因全局停顿操作而对TTFT（首Token时间）和TPOT（每Token输出时间）产生负面影响。我们的解决方案旨在最小化该操作带来的负面影响。"

msgid "## EPLB Effects"
msgstr "## EPLB 效果"

msgid ""
"- Reduced Latency: Dynamically balances expert loads to minimize TTFT and TPOT by distributing workloads evenly across experts.\n"
"- Adaptive Scaling: Automatically adjusts to workload fluctuations while maintaining stable performance."
msgstr ""
"- 降低延迟：通过在各专家间均匀分配工作负载，动态平衡专家负载以最小化TTFT和TPOT。\n"
"- 自适应扩展：自动适应工作负载波动，同时保持稳定的性能。"

msgid "## Support Scenarios"
msgstr "## 支持场景"

msgid "### Models"
msgstr "### 模型"

msgid ""
"All MOE models supported by vLLM-Ascend.\n"
"But we have only verified the performance on deepseek-v3.1/r1 models."
msgstr ""
"vLLM-Ascend支持的所有MOE模型。\n"
"但我们仅在deepseek-v3.1/r1模型上验证了性能。"

msgid "### MOE QuantType"
msgstr "### MOE量化类型"

msgid "## How to Use EPLB"
msgstr "## 如何使用EPLB"

msgid "EPLB has three usage modes:"
msgstr "EPLB有三种使用模式："

msgid ""
"> [!IMPORTANT]\n"
"> For Dynamic EPLB and Recording modes, the env variable acts as a safety guard: setting `dynamic_eplb: true` in config alone is not enough — the assertion requires `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`. Static EPLB (loading a pre-recorded map via `expert_map_path`) does **not** require an env variable."
msgstr ""
"> [!IMPORTANT]\n"
"> 对于动态EPLB和记录模式，环境变量充当安全防护：仅在配置中设置 `dynamic_eplb: true` 是不够的——断言要求必须设置 `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` 或 `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true`。静态EPLB（通过 `expert_map_path` 加载预记录映射）**不**需要环境变量。"

msgid "### Dynamic EPLB"
msgstr "### 动态EPLB"

msgid ""
"We need to add environment variable `export DYNAMIC_EPLB=\"true\"` to enable"
" vLLM-Ascend EPLB. Enable dynamic balancing with auto-tuned parameters. "
"Adjust expert_heat_collection_interval and algorithm_execution_interval "
"based on workload patterns. In the current version, we recommend using the "
"following: policy of swift balancer(2)."
msgstr ""
"我们需要添加环境变量 `export DYNAMIC_EPLB=\"true\"` 以启用vLLM-Ascend "
"EPLB。启用带自动调优参数的动态均衡。根据工作负载模式调整 expert_heat_collection_interval 和 "
"algorithm_execution_interval。在当前版本中，我们建议使用以下策略：swift balancer(2)。"

msgid "#### EPLB Policy Types"
msgstr "#### EPLB策略类型"

msgid ""
"The `eplb_policy_type` parameter selects the balancing algorithm used during"
" dynamic expert redistribution:"
msgstr "`eplb_policy_type` 参数选择动态专家重分配过程中使用的均衡算法："

msgid "### Static EPLB"
msgstr "### 静态EPLB"

msgid "#### Initial Setup (Record Expert Map)"
msgstr "#### 初始设置（记录专家映射）"

msgid ""
"We need to add environment variable `export EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"` to "
"record expert map. Generate the initial expert distribution map using "
"expert_map_record_path. This creates a baseline configuration for future "
"deployments."
msgstr ""
"我们需要添加环境变量 `export EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=\"true\"` 来记录专家映射。使用 "
"expert_map_record_path 生成初始专家分布映射。这将为后续部署创建基线配置。"

msgid "#### Subsequent Deployments (Use Recorded Map)"
msgstr "#### 后续部署（使用已记录的映射）"

msgid ""
"Load the pre-recorded expert map for consistent performance. This avoids "
"recalculating distributions at runtime."
msgstr "加载预记录的专家映射以获得一致的性能。这避免了在运行时重新计算分布。"

msgid "## Critical Considerations"
msgstr "## 关键注意事项"

msgid ""
"1. Parameter Tuning:\n"
"   - expert_heat_collection_interval: Higher values (e.g., 600+) for stable workloads; lower values (e.g., 50-100) for fluctuating traffic.\n"
"   - algorithm_execution_interval: Should be ≥ 50 to avoid premature balancing during startup.\n"
"   - num_redundant_experts: Must match (num_experts + num_redundant_experts) is divisible by expert-parallel size."
msgstr ""
"1. 参数调优：\n"
"   - expert_heat_collection_interval：对于稳定工作负载使用较高值（例如600+）；对于波动流量使用较低值（例如50-100）。\n"
"   - algorithm_execution_interval：应 ≥ 50，以避免启动期间过早进行均衡。\n"
"   - num_redundant_experts：必须满足 (num_experts + num_redundant_experts) 可被专家并行度整除。"

msgid ""
"2. Hardware Requirements:\n"
"   - Ensure that all NPUs have identical memory capacity and compute capabilities.\n"
"   - Network bandwidth must support expert redistribution traffic (≥ 10 Gbps recommended)."
msgstr ""
"2. 硬件要求：\n"
"   - 确保所有NPU具有相同的内存容量和计算能力。\n"
"   - 网络带宽必须支持专家重分配流量（建议≥10 Gbps）。"

msgid ""
"3. Monitoring & Validation:\n"
"   - Track metrics: Search for [Expert Hotness] in log, we will calculate the peak-to-average ratio of the load for each layer at different ranks, and then find their mean and maximum values. Current means actual peak-to-average ratio, update means estimated peak-to-average ratio after algorithm adjustment.\n"
"   - Use vLLM monitor to detect imbalances during runtime.\n"
"   - Always verify expert map JSON structure before loading (validate with jq or similar tools)."
msgstr ""
"3. 监控与验证：\n"
"   - 跟踪指标：在日志中搜索 [Expert Hotness]，我们将计算不同rank上每层负载的峰值均值比，然后找出其平均值和最大值。Current 表示实际峰值均值比，update 表示算法调整后的预估峰值均值比。\n"
"   - 使用vLLM监控器在运行时检测不均衡情况。\n"
"   - 加载前务必验证专家映射JSON结构（使用jq或类似工具进行验证）。"

msgid "| QuantType                       | Supported Hardware          |"
msgstr "| 量化类型                       | 支持的硬件                  |"

msgid "| Mode | Config in `eplb_config` | Env Variable |"
msgstr "| 模式 | `eplb_config` 中的配置 | 环境变量 |"

msgid "| Parameter | Description | Default |"
msgstr "| 参数 | 描述 | 默认值 |"

msgid "| Value | Policy | Description |"
msgstr "| 值 | 策略 | 描述 |"

msgid "| W8A8 / W8A8-Dynamic             | A2, A3 |"
msgstr "| W8A8 / W8A8-动态量化             | A2, A3 |"

msgid "| W4A8 (with fused MC2 enabled)   | A2, A3 |"
msgstr "| W4A8（启用融合MC2）   | A2, A3 |"

msgid "| MXFP4                           | Ascend 950 Products         |"
msgstr "| MXFP4                           | Ascend 950系列产品         |"

msgid "| MXFP8                           | Ascend 950 Products         |"
msgstr "| MXFP8                           | Ascend 950系列产品         |"

msgid "| **Dynamic EPLB** | `dynamic_eplb: true` | `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` |"
msgstr "| **动态EPLB** | `dynamic_eplb: true` | `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` |"

msgid ""
"| **Recording** (generate expert map) | `expert_map_record_path` | "
"`DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` or `EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true` |"
msgstr ""
"| **记录**（生成专家映射） | `expert_map_record_path` | `DYNAMIC_EPLB=true` 或 "
"`EXPERT_MAP_RECORD=true` |"

msgid ""
"| **Static EPLB** (load pre-recorded map) | `expert_map_path` | none "
"required |"
msgstr "| **静态EPLB**（加载预记录映射） | `expert_map_path` | 无需设置 |"

msgid "| dynamic_eplb | Enable dynamic EPLB. | False |"
msgstr "| dynamic_eplb | 启用动态EPLB。 | False |"

msgid ""
"| expert_heat_collection_interval | Interval for collecting expert heat. | "
"600 |"
msgstr "| expert_heat_collection_interval | 收集专家热度的间隔。 | 600 |"

msgid ""
"| algorithm_execution_interval | Interval for executing the balancing "
"algorithm. | 50 |"
msgstr "| algorithm_execution_interval | 执行均衡算法的间隔。 | 50 |"

msgid "| eplb_policy_type | EPLB policy type. | 2 |"
msgstr "| eplb_policy_type | EPLB策略类型。 | 2 |"

msgid "| num_redundant_experts | Number of redundant experts. | 0 |"
msgstr "| num_redundant_experts | 冗余专家数量。 | 0 |"

msgid ""
"| `0` | Random | Randomly swaps experts between ranks. Suitable for basic "
"testing only. |"
msgstr "| `0` | 随机 | 在rank之间随机交换专家。仅适用于基础测试。 |"

msgid ""
"| `1` | DefaultEplb | Open-source EPLB algorithm. Adds redundant experts to "
"the hottest, packs via balanced assignment with local constraint exchange. |"
msgstr "| `1` | DefaultEplb | 开源EPLB算法。为最热的专家添加冗余，通过带局部约束交换的均衡分配进行打包。 |"

msgid ""
"| `2` | SwiftBalanceEplb | Optimized for low-bandwidth environments. "
"Supports intra-node and inter-node expert redundancy, joint optimization of "
"expert placement. **(Recommended)** |"
msgstr ""
"| `2` | SwiftBalanceEplb | 针对低带宽环境优化。支持节点内和节点间专家冗余，联合优化专家放置。**（推荐）** |"

msgid ""
"| `3` | FlashLB | Statistical method using sliding-window "
"mean/variance/covariance of expert loads. Uses FlashTree layered search for "
"optimal replica allocation and `minimize_redeploy` for incremental "
"adjustment. Best for high-frequency load fluctuations. |"
msgstr ""
"| `3` | FlashLB | "
"使用专家负载的滑动窗口均值/方差/协方差的统计方法。利用FlashTree分层搜索进行最优副本分配，并使用`minimize_redeploy`进行增量调整。最适合高频负载波动场景。"
" |"
